WEBVTT

00:02.311 --> 00:03.689
Previously on "The Path"...

00:03.689 --> 00:04.775
‐ Why would you choose
a religion

00:04.775 --> 00:06.236
that would never choose you?

00:06.236 --> 00:07.739
‐ It's not just
about the religion, Hawk.

00:07.739 --> 00:09.492
It's about my family.
I‐it's everything.

00:09.492 --> 00:11.204
I will lose everything!

00:11.204 --> 00:13.500
Three women are accusing
you of groping them.

00:13.500 --> 00:14.962
You go.

00:14.962 --> 00:16.381
I can't run a session
like that.

00:16.381 --> 00:17.884
‐ Yes, you can help him
more than I can.

00:17.884 --> 00:19.721
‐ It's time
for the real work to begin.

00:19.721 --> 00:21.474
‐ Okay.

00:21.474 --> 00:23.103
What happened with Steve‐‐
Eddie will end this.

00:23.103 --> 00:24.565
‐ I don't want it
to end either.

00:24.565 --> 00:26.317
All the memories
are in there,

00:26.317 --> 00:28.405
in the cave
with he painted flowers.

00:28.405 --> 00:30.242
I just need to find it.

00:30.242 --> 00:33.039
Sarah and I have decided

00:33.039 --> 00:36.797
that, uh... she will no longer
be a part of The Movement.

00:36.797 --> 00:38.216
‐ Take this.

00:38.216 --> 00:39.970
It's what The Light
revealed to me.

00:39.970 --> 00:42.767
I'm just asking you
to sit down with her.

00:42.767 --> 00:44.938
She has a different story
of the beginning

00:44.938 --> 00:46.149
and the end.
‐ Where is she?

00:46.149 --> 00:47.527
She came out of surgery.

00:47.527 --> 00:49.113
I'm worried
something's happened.

00:49.113 --> 00:51.075
‐ Tell her I want to talk
to her immediately, okay?

00:51.075 --> 00:52.662
‐ So she doesn't know
that Eddie dies.

00:52.662 --> 00:55.208
Lilith is my mother.

00:55.208 --> 00:58.716
‐ You're telling me
that Steve is your father?

00:58.716 --> 01:01.429
‐ He's gonna die soon.
I saw it.

