‐ Eddie has to die.

36:30.099 --> 36:32.478
That's what she believes.

36:34.901 --> 36:36.486
‐ Why?

36:37.698 --> 36:40.913
‐ Well, he has
to bring Meyerism

36:40.913 --> 36:42.833
as high as it can go,

36:42.833 --> 36:45.463
and that's what
I was helping to do

36:45.463 --> 36:49.137
until I just couldn't anymore.

36:49.137 --> 36:50.473
The faith has to spread

36:50.473 --> 36:52.226
to as many people
as possible and...

36:56.443 --> 37:00.117
Well, The Movement will crumble
without Eddie, and...

37:00.117 --> 37:03.792
the world will crumble
without The Movement.

37:05.336 --> 37:08.843
I don't know why.
I don't understand.

37:08.843 --> 37:11.181
That's what she told me.
‐ Do you believe that?

37:11.181 --> 37:13.352
‐ I've decided not to.

37:13.352 --> 37:15.649
Yeah, but Lilith,
she will go to her grave

37:15.649 --> 37:18.530
convinced that Eddie
will go to his...

37:18.530 --> 37:20.324
and usher in the end of days.

37:20.324 --> 37:21.619
‐ Where is she?

37:30.011 --> 37:33.267
‐ Need anything else?
Coffee, pie, a milkshake?

37:33.267 --> 37:34.979
‐ No milkshake.

37:34.979 --> 37:37.400
‐ Just the check
would be great, thank you.

37:37.400 --> 37:39.572
‐
Such an asshole.

37:39.572 --> 37:41.324
I mean, I try to get him
out of that freak show,

37:41.324 --> 37:42.745
and he hits me?

37:42.745 --> 37:45.959
I mean, fuck him.
‐ Hey, stop it, okay?

37:45.959 --> 37:48.965
‐

37:48.965 --> 37:51.679
Yeah, you're right.

37:51.679 --> 37:54.350
I'm the asshole.

37:54.350 --> 37:56.021
I deserved to get
punched in the face.

37:56.021 --> 37:57.733
It's...
‐ No.

37:57.733 --> 38:01.824
This has nothing to do
with you and Caleb.

38:01.824 --> 38:04.037
I know you don't want
to hear that,

38:04.037 --> 38:06.291
but it's true.
‐

38:06.291 --> 38:08.838
‐ Okay?
This is all about Caleb

38:08.838 --> 38:10.508
and his father.

38:10.508 --> 38:12.888
‐ Yeah, but his dad's wrong.
Anyone can see that.

38:12.888 --> 38:17.523
‐ Look, Caleb wants his dad
to be so good so badly.

38:17.523 --> 38:19.693
And he wants to trust him,

38:19.693 --> 38:22.908
follow him,
believe in what he says.

38:22.908 --> 38:24.995
We all want that
to a certain extent.

38:27.543 --> 38:31.759
‐ I am... I am so sorry
I was rude to you.

38:31.759 --> 38:34.389
‐ It's all right, sweetheart.
I hate milkshakes, too.

38:46.329 --> 38:49.043
‐ Look, it takes
a lot of courage to admit

38:49.043 --> 38:53.845
that our fathers
have led us astray.

38:53.845 --> 38:58.061
For any of this to make sense,
for it...

38:58.061 --> 39:01.694
not all to feel so aimless...

39:04.073 --> 39:07.956
We want to trust
our parents have steered us

39:07.956 --> 39:10.336
in the right direction.

39:10.336 --> 39:15.597
So sometimes we go
to some pretty insane lengths,

39:15.597 --> 39:18.728
clearly, to make that so.

39:52.713 --> 39:54.507
It's been too long.

40:06.949 --> 40:08.745
‐ It's been hell

40:08.745 --> 40:12.418
since you first...
brought me here.

40:12.418 --> 40:14.505
I need to...

40:14.505 --> 40:18.180
be cleansed
of your entire...

40:20.894 --> 40:23.190
Of your entirety.

40:23.190 --> 40:25.904
‐ You're too hard on yourself.

40:45.735 --> 40:49.576
You're what stands
between me and my past.

40:59.387 --> 41:03.270
I need to cleanse
myself of you.

41:09.157 --> 41:13.165
‐
CAL: I shouldn't feel guilty...

41:13.165 --> 41:14.292
but I do.

41:15.670 --> 41:18.425
I shouldn't feel pride...

41:18.425 --> 41:21.974
- but I do.
- ‐

41:21.974 --> 41:26.191
I shouldn't feel shame,
but I do.

41:26.191 --> 41:28.028
‐

41:28.028 --> 41:32.161
‐

41:32.161 --> 41:34.207
I shouldn't feel love...

41:34.207 --> 41:36.044
‐

41:36.044 --> 41:37.631
But I do.

41:37.631 --> 41:41.680
‐
‐

41:43.684 --> 41:46.314
‐

42:12.951 --> 42:14.830
‐ Buck?

42:17.251 --> 42:18.629
Buck?

42:39.462 --> 42:42.259
‐ I often wish
I was a kid again.

42:42.259 --> 42:45.098
‐ I think we all do‐‐
just with better childhoods

42:45.098 --> 42:47.854
than the ones we actually had.

42:47.854 --> 42:49.231
‐ Yeah.

42:51.945 --> 42:55.077
Someday you'll have to tell me
about yours.

42:59.210 --> 43:02.592
Hey, I...

43:02.592 --> 43:04.763
I'm sorry about last night.

43:04.763 --> 43:06.432
‐ I'm sure you say that
to all the girls...

43:06.432 --> 43:08.144
and their lawyers.

43:08.144 --> 43:10.608
No, we, uh... we had fun.

43:13.531 --> 43:15.117
‐ Hey, let's go get
some breakfast.

43:15.117 --> 43:16.662
You can pay me back
for the fries.

43:16.662 --> 43:17.997
‐ I will pay you back,

43:17.997 --> 43:19.710
but I think
we should stay here.

43:19.710 --> 43:22.716
Morning‐after pancakes
is not a good look, PR‐wise.

43:22.716 --> 43:25.095
‐ Ah, you're right.
Okay.

43:25.095 --> 43:27.600
‐ Well... a room service life.

43:27.600 --> 43:30.313
‐ Well, it's what
you signed up for.

43:36.409 --> 43:38.998
‐ Hey.

43:38.998 --> 43:42.337
How'd it go?

43:42.337 --> 43:45.385
‐
‐ Did Caleb come back with you?

43:45.385 --> 43:49.477
‐ No, he, uh... he stayed.

43:49.477 --> 43:52.692
‐ Oh, that's, um‐‐
that's awful.

43:54.529 --> 43:57.535
Hey, um...
Eddie, I, um...

43:58.788 --> 44:02.085
I wanted to tell you something.

44:02.085 --> 44:05.927
My mother...
I had her put away in this‐‐

44:05.927 --> 44:08.348
‐ No, don't. Look...

44:08.348 --> 44:10.519
you don't have to tell me.

44:10.519 --> 44:13.274
Okay?
Not now.

44:13.274 --> 44:16.364
You can tell me later.

44:16.364 --> 44:20.665
Look, it's just been
a very... long night,

44:20.665 --> 44:24.965
and I don't want to
be mad at you anymore.

44:26.342 --> 44:31.687
I am extremely mad
at Steve, and...

44:31.687 --> 44:34.400
I don't know what
to do with that.

44:34.400 --> 44:36.905
‐ I'm sorry.

44:36.905 --> 44:39.076
It makes me sad.

44:39.076 --> 44:40.746
‐ Yeah, me too.

44:40.746 --> 44:43.293
‐ All of it.

44:48.596 --> 44:51.183
‐ Mm.
‐ Let's just...

44:52.604 --> 44:54.649
Be us, okay?

44:54.649 --> 44:56.820
Just for a little while.

44:56.820 --> 44:59.199
Just here...

44:59.199 --> 45:01.454
now, us...

45:01.454 --> 45:03.207
‐ Mm.
‐ And not them.

45:24.751 --> 45:28.091
‐ Sarah.

45:28.091 --> 45:30.846
I just knew you would find me.

45:32.182 --> 45:35.815
I'm so indebted to you.

45:35.815 --> 45:39.238
‐ You never told me
that Vera was your daughter...

45:39.238 --> 45:40.992
or that Steve was her father.

45:40.992 --> 45:42.369
‐ I know.

45:42.369 --> 45:44.415
And that was terribly
wrong of me.

45:44.415 --> 45:45.668
‐ Wrong?

45:45.668 --> 45:48.131
‐ I wanted you
to know the work,

45:48.131 --> 45:50.553
not what was happening
in my personal life.

45:50.553 --> 45:53.224
‐ I wanted to believe
that The Light spoke to you.

45:55.270 --> 45:58.359
‐ It did.

45:58.359 --> 46:02.660
And I think you know that.

46:02.660 --> 46:05.373
‐ I don't know anything.

46:05.373 --> 46:07.085
‐ Then you wouldn't be here.

46:07.085 --> 46:08.881
You wouldn't have
tracked me down.

46:08.881 --> 46:12.054
I think you need
to set things right.

46:12.054 --> 46:14.768
‐ I do need
to set things right.

46:14.768 --> 46:16.730
‐ Vera put me in here,

46:16.730 --> 46:19.485
and she's the only one
who can get me out.

46:19.485 --> 46:22.115
‐ I think you're
right where you need to be.

46:22.115 --> 46:24.411
‐ No, you need...

46:24.411 --> 46:26.082
You have to do
something about this.

46:26.082 --> 46:27.585
If not,
you're no better than them.

46:27.585 --> 46:29.547
You're no better than Steve.

46:29.547 --> 46:31.133
Sarah!

46:34.933 --> 46:37.270
Get me out of here!

47:20.148 --> 47:23.404
‐ Hey.
‐ Ah, he returns.

47:23.404 --> 47:26.160
Welcome back. Um...

47:26.160 --> 47:28.414
Not much to report,

47:28.414 --> 47:30.628
but, uh, I can give you
a debrief

47:30.628 --> 47:32.882
on what you've missed
if you'd like.

47:35.220 --> 47:38.059
‐ Something happen, Cal?

47:38.059 --> 47:40.188
‐ Happen...

47:40.188 --> 47:41.942
‐ To you...

47:43.402 --> 47:44.948
With Steve.

47:49.666 --> 47:52.212
‐ How‐‐um...

47:52.212 --> 47:54.383
‐ You don't have to tell me.

47:59.978 --> 48:02.107
‐ No, I, um...

48:12.920 --> 48:15.049
Pray with me?

48:20.018 --> 48:22.063
‐ You still want
to be a Meyerist?

48:25.403 --> 48:27.198
‐ I shouldn't.

48:30.204 --> 48:32.543
But I do.

